Doubt can only be removed by action. 

#workout #hardwork #aesthetic #darkaesthetic #entrepreneurship

It’s getting insanely saturated and flooded out there with self help tips and tricks to become the best version of yourself… While these kinds of things aren’t the worst, they can have the reverse effect that they are intended for. The more tactics and techniques you try to implement into your daily routine, the more complicated and foggy your focus/intentions become. Often times, These tips and tricks serve as excuses to not get the real work done. The stuff you and I both know we don’t want to do… But it must get done in order to progress.

I’d like to suggest a different approach from everything you see across IG and TikTok every day - be simple. Cut things out that you don’t need and get the work done. Stop acting ‘busy’. Stop procrastinating. Attack what needs to be done now and be happy you did so later on. 

No “hack” is going to get you out of the rut you’re currently in. All these “hacks” are going to do is force you spend more time not doing what you actually need to. 

Put down the phone and do what’s required. Let’s be real - you know exactly what you need to do, you are simply just avoiding it.
